      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3, powered by the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power plant features eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, delivering 414 hp through a crisp 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. The chassis integrity remains excellent, utilizing M-specific aluminum subframes and a 3.85 final drive ratio with the M Variable Differential Lock for superior lateral kinematics. The Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides three distinct valve-mapping profiles, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and five-link rear suspension remain planted. Crucially, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been inspected, ensuring this S65 retains its high-frequency harmonic balance. A driver-spec example that prioritizes mechanical feedback and powertrain linearity.",
